                <Header>Climate Change</Header>
                <Paragraph>The AFDB promotes building greater capacity for African countries to address climate change risks. The AFDB finances investments that are "climate-proof," meaning that these investments are designed, installed, implemented, and managed to reduce to a minimal level global warming's adverse effects, while maintaining the most cost-effective ratio as possible.</Paragraph>
